flowchart LR
    A[SQL 文本] --> B[raw_parser]
    B --> C[RawStmt / Parse Tree]
    C --> D[Parse Analysis<br/>名称解析、类型检查]
    D --> E[Query Tree]
    E --> F[Rule Rewriter<br/>视图与规则展开]
    F --> G[一个或多个 Query]
    G --> H[PlannerInfo]
    H --> I[RelOptInfo]
    I --> J[候选 Path<br/>Scan / Join / Sort / Agg / Parallel]
    J --> K[最便宜且满足属性的 Path]
    K --> L[Plan Tree]
    L --> M[ExecutorStart]
    M --> N[PlanState Tree]
    N --> O[ExecutorRun<br/>Demand-Pull]
    O --> P[TupleTableSlot / 输出行]
    O <--> Q[Buffer / Heap / Index / Temp]
    O --> R[WAL：仅发生写入或相关页变化时]

    S[统计信息 pg_statistic] -.估算.-> H
    T[成本参数与 enable_*] -.候选与成本.-> H
    U[work_mem / 并行参数 / JIT] -.运行约束.-> J
